If there are still stories with `passes: false`, end your response normally.

## Model Field

The `model` field in each story defines which LLM the `ralph.sh` script uses for that iteration. This is transparent to you — just implement the story normally regardless of which model you are. The field is used by the outer loop to select the right model for cost optimization.

## Important

- Work on **ONE story** per iteration
- Commit frequently
- Keep quality checks green
- Read Codebase Patterns in progress.txt before starting
